## 5. Pipeline ops — user ถามสถานะ / queue / stations / ads

**อ่านก่อน:** `.agents/skills/pipeline-ops/SKILL.md`

รันชุด diagnostic นี้เอง:

```powershell
cd h:\DEV\projects\radio-ad-sensing-pipeline
.\scripts\pipeline-status.ps1
docker compose -f docker-compose.yml -f docker-compose.prod.yml -f docker-compose.windows-dev.yml ps
docker logs radio-worker --tail 15
docker logs radio-ingestor --tail 15
```

**CRITICAL:** อย่าอ่าน `data/pipeline.db` จาก Windows host ตอน Docker ingest ทำงาน — ใช้:

```powershell
docker exec radio-worker python -c "import sqlite3; c=sqlite3.connect('/app/data/pipeline.db'); print(c.execute('SELECT status, COUNT(*) FROM chunks GROUP BY status').fetchall()); c.close()"
```

| Trigger | คำสั่งเพิ่ม |
|---|---|
| enabled stations | `docker exec radio-ingestor python -c "from shared.config import load_stations; print([s.name for s in load_stations() if s.enabled])"` |
| keyword hits | `docker exec radio-worker python -c "import sqlite3; c=sqlite3.connect('/app/data/pipeline.db'); print(c.execute('SELECT keyword, COUNT(*) n FROM keyword_hits GROUP BY keyword ORDER BY n DESC LIMIT 15').fetchall()); c.close()"` |
| schema probe | `docker exec radio-worker python -c "import sqlite3; c=sqlite3.connect('/app/data/pipeline.db'); [print(r) for r in c.execute('PRAGMA table_info(chunks)').fetchall()]; c.close()"` |
| Ollama models | `docker exec radio-worker python -c "import urllib.request,json; d=json.loads(urllib.request.urlopen('http://radio-ollama:11434/api/tags',timeout=5).read()); [print(m.get('name')) for m in d.get('models',[])]"` |

Dashboard URL (compose up): `http://127.0.0.1:8081`

**Ask user ก่อนทำ:** แก้ `stations.yaml`, `docker compose down`, restart services, แก้ production DB, commit/push, อ่าน `.env`

